Field Detail

OP_LOCATIONPATH

public static final byte OP_LOCATIONPATH
Represents a LocationPath: Word-code usage: (code to evaluate step1 - in forward direction, not RPN)) ... (code to evaluate stepN - in forward direction, not RPN)) [start of step1, relative to OP_LOCATIONPATH pc] ... [start of stepN, relative to OP_LOCATIONPATH pc] [number of steps (i.e. N)] [OP_LOCATIONPATH]

OP_EXPR_LOCATIONPATH

public static final byte OP_EXPR_LOCATIONPATH
Represents a FilterExpr followed by a '/' or '//' and RelativeLocationPath: Word-code usage: (code for FilterExpr) (code to evaluate step1 - in forward direction, not RPN)) ... (code to evaluate stepn - in forward direction, not RPN)) [start of step1, relative to OP_EXPR_LOCATIONPATH pc] ... [start of stepN, relative to OP_EXPR_LOCATIONPATH pc] [number of steps (i.e. N)] [OP_EXPR_LOCATIONPATH]

OP_NODE

public static final byte OP_NODE
The NodeType operator 'node()'. As a lexical token, represents 'node' followed by '('.

OP_ROOT

public static final byte OP_ROOT
The NodeType operator for the document root. As a lexical token, represents an initial '/'.

OP_COMMENT

public static final byte OP_COMMENT
The NodeType operator 'comment()'. As a lexical token, represents 'comment' followed by '('.

OP_TEXT

public static final byte OP_TEXT
The NodeType operator 'text()'. As a lexical token, represents 'text' followed by '('.

OP_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION

public static final byte OP_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION
The NodeType operator 'processing-instructor([Name])'. As a lexical token, represents 'processing-instruction' followed by '('. Wordcode usage: [OP_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION] [index of Name in values table, or -1]

ANY_RESULT

public static final int ANY_RESULT
A result of any type. As a result code, means result is in context's objResult field.

STRING_RESULT

public static final int STRING_RESULT
A string result. As a request code, tells eval to leave a String result in objResult. As a result code, means result is a String in context's objResult field.

NODESET_RESULT

public static final int NODESET_RESULT
A node-set result. As a result code, means result is a NodeList in context's objResult field.

BOOLEAN_RESULT

public static final int BOOLEAN_RESULT
A boolean result. As a result code, means result is in context's boolResult field. As a request code, tells eval to leave result in boolResult.

PREDICATE_RESULT

public static final int PREDICATE_RESULT
A boolean result, but an number is matches againt position(). Invalid as a result code. As a request code, tells eval to convert numbers to booleans by comparing with position(), and to leave result in boolResult.

NUMBER_RESULT

public static final int NUMBER_RESULT
A numeric result. As a result code, means result is in context's numResult field. As a request code, tells eval to leave result in numResult.

COUNT_RESULT

public static final int COUNT_RESULT
A numeric result. As a request code, tells eval to increment numResult for each node.
